# Example Document ## 1. Selection Marks (Checkboxes) Employee Preferences Form ☐ Remote ☒ Hybrid ☐ On-site ## 2. Barcodes Go check out Azure AI Content Understanding at the below link HELLOWORLD ## 3. Formulas Bayesian Inference (Posterior Probability): $$P \left( \theta \mid D \right) = \frac { P \left( D \mid \theta \right) \cdot P \left( \theta \right) } { P \left( D \right) }$$ Where: $P \left( \theta \mid D \right)$ is the posterior $P \left( D \mid \theta \right)$ is the likelihood $P \left( \theta \right)$ is the prior $P \left( D \right)$ is the evidence ## 4. Images Sample Product Image Image Description: "A ceramic coffee mug with company logo." ## 5. Tables
Category Amount ($)
Rent 1,200

Transportation 100
Total 1,750
## 6. Paragraphs Our company is committed to fostering a productive and inclusive work environment. All employees are expected to comply with the outlined policies and demonstrate mutual respect in day-to-day operations. Regular reviews will ensure that these policies remain relevant and effective.
